Cloning phase2 locally and running the test which failed also fails for me.

JUnit4 Test Runner
...............E
Time: 0.083
There was 1 failure:
1) testUInt8Tensor(org.tensorflow.TensorTest)
java.lang.IllegalArgumentException: class org.tensorflow.types.TFUInt8 is not a TensorFlow type.
        at org.tensorflow.types.Types.dataType(Types.java:40)
        at org.tensorflow.Tensor.create(Tensor.java:117)
        at org.tensorflow.TensorTest.testUInt8Tensor(TensorTest.java:423)
...

It ain't lying... the static block in org.tensorflow.types.Types does not register the org.tensorflow.types.TFUInt8 class in its zeroes and typeCodes maps.

body:
Cloning `phase2` locally and running the test which failed also fails for me.
```
JUnit4 Test Runner
...............E
Time: 0.083
There was 1 failure:
1) testUInt8Tensor(org.tensorflow.TensorTest)
java.lang.IllegalArgumentException: class org.tensorflow.types.TFUInt8 is not a TensorFlow type.
        at org.tensorflow.types.Types.dataType(Types.java:40)
        at org.tensorflow.Tensor.create(Tensor.java:117)
        at org.tensorflow.TensorTest.testUInt8Tensor(TensorTest.java:423)
...
```
It ain't lying... the static block in `org.tensorflow.types.Types` does not register the `org.tensorflow.types.TFUInt8` class in its `zeroes` and `typeCodes` maps.
